Akko CS Wine Red Linear Switch (Lubed, 45pcs)


6925758618250

Normal price€14,99
plus sales tax + shipping costs

Description：New now

  • 【The hand-lubed version CS Switch】Compared with the regular version, the hand-lubed version CS Switch is improved, the shaft rail and the cylinder of the lower case are hand-lubricated in addition to the dry film lubrication on the shaft and spring, and the machine lubrication on the sheet metal corners same as the regular CS switches；
  • 【Compatible with MX Structure Keycaps】 AKKO CS switches are designed with general MX structure, so they can fit most (X) cross shank keycap sets. This greatly improves compatibility and you can always change the switch and recreate your own keyboard；
  • 【Built-in LED Slot&Durable Lifespan】AKKO CS switches are designed with north-facing LED slot for LED modification. It is also compatible with SMD LED. This offers more fun features and options for those who are DIYers. With a lifespan of approximately 50 million keystrokes based on lab durability testing, you can be assured of a long service life.
